      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 represents the pinnacle of naturally aspirated longitudinal dynamics. Powered by the S54 3.2L straight-six, it utilizes individual throttle bodies and a high-pressure VANOS system to deliver linear power up to an 8,000 RPM redline. The Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox pairs seamlessly with a limited-slip differential for precise torque vectoring. The chassis is well-sorted, maintaining excellent torsional rigidity and featuring a multi-link rear suspension that provides surgical turn-in. While showing minor signs of road use consistent with its age, the mechanical components\u2014including the cooling system and subframe mounting points\u2014remain in strong operational order. A mechanically honest example for the discerning driver.",
